---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Week 6: 張力と弾性力">
  <h1>Week 6: 張力と弾性力</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">ばねの「倔強（頑固さ）」を測ろう！</p>

  <h2>🎯 今日の目標</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>糸の張力を理解する</li>
    <li>フックの法則（F = kx）を使える</li>
    <li>ばねの直列・並列を計算できる</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>張力 T</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    糸やロープが物体を <strong>引っ張る力</strong>
  </div>

  <h3>張力の特徴</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>糸に沿った方向にはたらく</li>
    <li>軽くて伸びない糸では、糸全体で張力は <strong>同じ</strong></li>
    <li>滑車を通しても大きさは変わらない</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例：鉛直につるす</h4>
    <p>重さ W の物体を糸でつるす → 張力 T = W = mg</p>
  </div>

  <h2>弾性力（フックの法則）</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    ばねが変形したとき、<strong>元に戻ろうとする力</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">F = kx</span>
    <p>弾性力 = ばね定数 × 伸び（縮み）</p>
  </div>

  <table>
    <tr><th>記号</th><th>意味</th><th>単位</th></tr>
    <tr><td>F</td><td>弾性力</td><td>N</td></tr>
    <tr><td>k</td><td>ばね定数（硬さ）</td><td>N/m</td></tr>
    <tr><td>x</td><td>伸び（または縮み）</td><td>m</td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="highlight-box warning">
    <strong>⚠️ 注意：</strong>x は「伸びた長さ」であって「全体の長さ」ではない！
  </div>

  <h3>ばね定数 k の意味</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>k が大きい</strong> → 硬いばね（伸ばすのに大きな力が必要）</li>
    <li><strong>k が小さい</strong> → 柔らかいばね</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>🎮 ばねシミュレーター</h3>
  <div class="animation-container">
    <div id="spring-sim">
      <div class="spring-area">
        <div class="spring-mount">🔩</div>
        <div class="spring" id="spring-visual">〰️〰️〰️</div>
        <div class="weight-area">
          <select id="weight-select">
            <option value="0">なし</option>
            <option value="1">1 kg</option>
            <option value="2">2 kg</option>
            <option value="3">3 kg</option>
            <option value="4">4 kg</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="spring-graph">
        <canvas id="springCanvas" width="200" height="150"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="spring-info">
        <p>ばね定数 k = <strong>20 N/m</strong></p>
        <p>伸び x = <span id="spring-x">0</span> m</p>
        <p>弾性力 F = <span id="spring-f">0</span> N</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>ばねの直列・並列</h2>

  <h3>直列接続（縦につなぐ）</h3>
  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">1/k合 = 1/k₁ + 1/k₂</span>
    <p>合成ばね定数が <strong>小さく</strong> なる（柔らかくなる）</p>
  </div>

  <h3>並列接続（横につなぐ）</h3>
  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">k合 = k₁ + k₂</span>
    <p>合成ばね定数が <strong>大きく</strong> なる（硬くなる）</p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>💡 覚え方</h4>
    <p><strong>直列</strong>（手をつなぐ）→ お互い助け合って伸びやすい → <strong>柔らかく</strong></p>
    <p><strong>並列</strong>（肩を組む）→ 力を合わせて踏ん張る → <strong>硬く</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>例題</h2>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題1：ばね定数を求める</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>1.0 N の力でばねを引くと 0.05 m 伸びた。ばね定数は？</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>k = F/x = 1.0 ÷ 0.05 = <strong>20 N/m</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題2：伸びを求める</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>k = 20 N/m のばねに 2.0 N の力を加えると？</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>x = F/k = 2.0 ÷ 20 = <strong>0.10 m</strong>（10 cm）</p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題3：直列ばね</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>k₁ = 20 N/m、k₂ = 30 N/m を直列につなぐと？</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>1/k合 = 1/20 + 1/30 = 3/60 + 2/60 = 5/60 = 1/12</p>
    <p>k合 = <strong>12 N/m</strong>（元より柔らかい！）</p>
  </div>

  <h2>練習問題</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>問題</th><th>解答</th></tr>
    <tr>
      <td>① k = 50 N/m のばねを 0.2 m 伸ばす力は？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>F = 50 × 0.2 = 10 N</details></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>② 3 N で 0.1 m 伸びるばねの k は？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>k = 3 ÷ 0.1 = 30 N/m</details></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>③ k = 10 と k = 10 を並列にすると？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>k合 = 10 + 10 = 20 N/m</details></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2>📝 今日のポイント</h2>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    <ul>
      <li>✓ 張力：糸が引っ張る力（糸に沿う方向）</li>
      <li>✓ フックの法則：<strong>F = kx</strong></li>
      <li>✓ 直列：1/k合 = 1/k₁ + 1/k₂（柔らかくなる）</li>
      <li>✓ 並列：k合 = k₁ + k₂（硬くなる）</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week05/" class="nav-btn secondary">← Week 5</a>
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week07/" class="nav-btn">Week 7 へ →</a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }
  .formula-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .big-formula {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    display: block;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  #spring-sim {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 200px;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .spring-area {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .spring-mount {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .spring {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .weight-area select {
    padding: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .spring-graph {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  #springCanvas {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: white;
  }
  .spring-info {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .spring-info p {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  details summary {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    #spring-sim {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const select = document.getElementById('weight-select') as HTMLSelectElement;
  const spring = document.getElementById('spring-visual');
  const springX = document.getElementById('spring-x');
  const springF = document.getElementById('spring-f');
  const canvas = document.getElementById('springCanvas') as HTMLCanvasElement;
  const ctx = canvas?.getContext('2d');

  const k = 20; // N/m
  const g = 10;
  const points: {x: number, f: number}[] = [];

  function updateSpring() {
    const mass = parseInt(select?.value || '0');
    const force = mass * g;
    const x = force / k;

    if (springX) springX.textContent = x.toFixed(2);
    if (springF) springF.textContent = force.toString();

    // Animate spring stretch
    if (spring) {
      const stretch = 1 + x * 2;
      spring.style.transform = `scaleY(${stretch})`;
    }

    // Add point to graph
    if (mass > 0) {
      points.push({ x, f: force });
    }
    drawGraph();
  }

  function drawGraph() {
    if (!ctx) return;
    ctx.clearRect(0, 0, 200, 150);

    // Axes
    ctx.strokeStyle = '#64748b';
    ctx.lineWidth = 1;
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(30, 130);
    ctx.lineTo(190, 130);
    ctx.moveTo(30, 130);
    ctx.lineTo(30, 10);
    ctx.stroke();

    // Labels
    ctx.fillStyle = '#64748b';
    ctx.font = '12px sans-serif';
    ctx.fillText('x (m)', 170, 145);
    ctx.fillText('F (N)', 5, 20);

    // Ideal line (F = kx)
    ctx.strokeStyle = '#dbeafe';
    ctx.lineWidth = 2;
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(30, 130);
    ctx.lineTo(30 + 0.2 * 400, 130 - 40 * 2);
    ctx.stroke();

    // Points
    ctx.fillStyle = '#2563eb';
    points.forEach(p => {
      const px = 30 + p.x * 400;
      const py = 130 - p.f * 2;
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.arc(px, py, 5, 0, Math.PI * 2);
      ctx.fill();
    });

    // Connect points
    if (points.length > 1) {
      ctx.strokeStyle = '#22c55e';
      ctx.lineWidth = 2;
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.moveTo(30, 130);
      points.forEach(p => {
        ctx.lineTo(30 + p.x * 400, 130 - p.f * 2);
      });
      ctx.stroke();
    }
  }

  select?.addEventListener('change', updateSpring);
  drawGraph();
</script>
